## PR template
## 📝 PR 描述 (Description)

请简要描述此 PR 解决的问题或新增的功能。如果关联了具体的 Issue，请使用 `Fixes #Issue号` 的格式。

## 🛠️ 变更类型 (Type of change)

- [ ] 🐛 Bug 修复 (Bug fix)
- [ ] ✨ 新功能 (New feature)
- [ ] ♻️ 代码重构 (Refactoring)
- [ ] 🚀 性能优化 (Performance improvement)
- [ ] 📚 文档更新 (Documentation update)

## 🛡️ 自检清单 (Checklist)

提交 PR 前，请确保你已经完成了以下自检：

- [ ] 我已经阅读并遵循了项目的架构与编码规范。
- [ ] 我在本地成功运行了 `pnpm governance:gate`。
- [ ] 我在本地成功运行了 `pnpm type-check` 且零报错。
- [ ] 我在本地成功运行了 `pnpm lint:check`。
- [ ] 如更新 `.ai/governance/**`、`docs/generated/**` 或公共 exports，我已提交同步后的生成物。
- [ ] 如更新视觉快照，我已用 `pnpm e2e:update` 单独生成并审查 baseline，CI 仅运行验证不会自动更新快照。
- [ ] 我的代码变更没有引入新的警告（Console warnings）。

## 📎 补充说明 (Additional context)

如果有需要评审者特别注意的代码逻辑或视觉 UI 变更截图，请补充在这里。

## CI workflow
name: CI Guardian

on:
  push:
    branches: [main, develop]
  pull_request:
    branches: [main]

env:
  FORCE_JAVASCRIPT_ACTIONS_TO_NODE24: 'true'

concurrency:
  group: ci-${{ github.ref }}
  cancel-in-progress: true

jobs:
  quality:
    name: Core Quality
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    env:
      NODE_OPTIONS: '--max-old-space-size=4096'

    steps:
      - name: Checkout codebase
        uses: actions/checkout@v6
        with:
          fetch-depth: 0
        env:
          GIT_CONFIG_COUNT: '1'
          GIT_CONFIG_KEY_0: init.defaultBranch
          GIT_CONFIG_VALUE_0: main

      - name: Block WIP commits on main
        if: github.event_name == 'pull_request'
        run: |
          if git log --format='%s' origin/main..HEAD | grep -qiE '^wip(\(.*\))?:'; then
            echo "::error::❌ WIP commits detected! Please squash or reword before merging to main."
            exit 1
          fi

      - name: Install pnpm
        uses: pnpm/action-setup@v5
        with:
          version: 10.28.2
        env:
          NODE_NO_WARNINGS: '1'

      - name: Setup Node.js
        uses: actions/setup-node@v6
        with:
          node-version: 24.x
          cache: 'pnpm'

      - name: Deterministic Frozen Install
        run: bash scripts/exec.sh pnpm install --frozen-lockfile

      - name: Authorize GitHub CLI
        run: echo "${{ github.token }}" | gh auth login --with-token

      # repair_list.md is local runtime state and created by ai:sync from the Markdown template; doctor requires it.
      - name: CI runtime summary
        run: bash scripts/exec.sh pnpm runtime:summary

      - name: Sync AI adapters (materialize local runtime)
        run: bash scripts/exec.sh pnpm ai:sync

      - name: Prepare internal workspace packages
        run: bash scripts/exec.sh pnpm ci:prepare-internal

      - name: AI Architecture Doctor
        run: bash scripts/exec.sh pnpm ai:doctor

      - name: Unified Governance Gate
        run: bash scripts/exec.sh pnpm validate:governance

      - name: Verify Generated AI Artifacts Are Synced
        run: |
          bash scripts/exec.sh pnpm ai:sync
          bash scripts/exec.sh pnpm ai:sync:codex
          if ! git diff --quiet -- AGENTS.md CLAUDE.md .ai/manifests/skills-lock.json; then
            echo "::error::Generated AI artifacts are stale. Run pnpm ai:sync && pnpm ai:sync:codex and commit the results."
            git diff -- AGENTS.md CLAUDE.md .ai/manifests/skills-lock.json
            exit 1
          fi

      - name: Strict Type Check
        run: bash scripts/exec.sh pnpm type-check

      - name: Unit Tests
        run: bash scripts/exec.sh pnpm test:run

      - name: Strict Lint Check
        run: bash scripts/exec.sh pnpm lint:check

      - name: Production Build Test
        run: bash scripts/exec.sh pnpm exec turbo run build

      - name: Desktop Bundle Guard
        run: |
          bash scripts/exec.sh pnpm build:desktop
          bash scripts/exec.sh pnpm budget:desktop

  e2e-qa:
    name: E2E QA
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    env:
      NODE_OPTIONS: '--max-old-space-size=4096'

    steps:
      - name: Checkout codebase
        uses: actions/checkout@v6
        with:
          fetch-depth: 0
        env:
          GIT_CONFIG_COUNT: '1'
          GIT_CONFIG_KEY_0: init.defaultBranch
          GIT_CONFIG_VALUE_0: main

      - name: Install pnpm
        uses: pnpm/action-setup@v5
        with:
          version: 10.28.2
        env:
          NODE_NO_WARNINGS: '1'

      - name: Setup Node.js
        uses: actions/setup-node@v6
        with:
          node-version: 24.x
          cache: 'pnpm'

      - name: Deterministic Frozen Install
        run: bash scripts/exec.sh pnpm install --frozen-lockfile

      - name: Install Playwright Chromium
        run: bash scripts/exec.sh pnpm exec playwright install --with-deps chromium

      - name: Prepare internal workspace packages
        run: bash scripts/exec.sh pnpm ci:prepare-internal

      - name: Run Playwright QA suite
        run: bash scripts/exec.sh pnpm e2e:qa

